ygData.subject: Re: SBS Report
ygData.msgSnippet: Ah Les, why a sudden change of weap? Or is it for ya necro char? ;)
ygData.messageBody:
Ah Les, why a sudden change of weap? Or is it for ya necro char? ;)


On Friday, 02 July, 1999 6:53 PM, Leshrec [SMTP:leshrec@...] wrote:
> From: "Leshrec" <leshrec@...>
>
> Hmm How many SBS do you all need? I can gate to faydark and camp there for a
> day. I need the dirk that is loaded with DVinn so I can try to get some SBS
> too. Prolly i can get 1 or maybe lucky 2..
>
> -----Original Message-----
> From: LKW <leekw13@...>
> To: '* Singapore EQ Mailing List' <sg-everquest@onelist.com>
> Date: Friday, July 02, 1999 9:26 AM
> Subject: [sg-everquest] SBS Report
>
>
> >From: LKW <leekw13@...>
> >
> >Just to inform all kakis abt our SBS hunt in CB.
> >
> >After killing more than 15 trainers, we only managed to get one SBS on the
> >13th trainer. The SBS is given to Einan, our only local kakis cleric. Due
> >to time constraint, we are unable to hunt for more. Furthermore, becoz of
> >the anti camp thingy that was implemented, the spawning of SBS are even
> >more rare.
> >
> >Nevertheless I will con't to look for more SBS for local kakis like
> >Trifrost, Sereph and other tanks once I go back Faydark.
> >
> >Tonight is Friday night, as per usual I will be training at NRo derv camp
> >next to mountain till morning. All kakis who wish to join me are most
> >welcome to do so.
